def job_titles(conn):
    cur = conn.cursor()
    cur.execute('
        SELECT job_title
        FROM employees
        GROUP BY job_title
        HAVING COUNT(*) >= 10 AND AVG(salary) >= 50000
        ORDER BY AVG(salary) DESC
    ')
    return [row[1] for row in cur.fetchall()]
